%% vLLM CPU - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>HTTPS/TLS
    participant API as vLLM OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine<br/>PagedAttention
    participant CPU as CPU Kernels (C++)<br/>AVX/NEON/VSX/VXE
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over API,CPU: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer API Key
    Gateway->>API: Forward Request<br/>Optional TLS
    API->>Engine: Submit Inference Task<br/>Python IPC
    Engine->>CPU: Execute Attention Kernels<br/>C++ Binding
    CPU-->>Engine: Computed Tensors
    Engine-->>API: Generation Result
    API-->>Gateway: JSON Response (or SSE Stream)
    Gateway-->>Client: Response

    Note over API,CPU: Flow 2: gRPC Inference (Rust Router)

    participant Router as Rust Router
    Router->>API: VllmEngine.Generate<br/>gRPC/50051 plaintext
    Note right of API: gRPC Server<br/>Port 50051
    API->>Engine: Submit Inference Task<br/>Python IPC
    Engine->>CPU: Execute Attention Kernels<br/>C++ Binding
    CPU-->>Engine: Computed Tensors
    Engine-->>API: Generation Result
    API-->>Router: gRPC Streaming Response<br/>plaintext

    Note over Engine,HF: Flow 3: Model Loading

    Engine->>HF: Download Model Weights<br/>HTTPS/443, HF Token
    HF-->>Engine: Model Artifacts
    Note over Engine: Load into CPU Memory<br/>via PagedAttention

    participant Prom as Prometheus
    Prom->>API: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000
    API-->>Prom: Prometheus Metrics
